text: Kara-Döbö may refer to the following places in Kyrgyzstan: *Kara-Döbö, Batken, a village in Kadamjay District, Batken Region *Kara-Döbö, Chuy, a village in Chuy District, Chuy Region *Kara-Döbö, Jayyl, a village in Jayyl District, Chuy Region *Kara-Döbö, Jalal-Abad, a village in Aksy District, Jalal-Abad Region *Kara-Döbö, Osh, a village in Kara-Suu District, Osh Region
title: Kara-Döbö
